ws.\nL&T lost 20% over Middle East exposure risks, IndiGo dropped 16% from flight cancellations and fuel costs, while HPCL fell 25% amid crude price spikes.","summary":"The 2026 Iran war impacted Indian stocks, with L&T, IndiGo, and HPCL facing declines due to disrupted oil supply, trade routes, and investor outflows.\nL&T lost 20% over Middle East exposure risks, IndiGo dropped 16% from flight cancellations and fuel costs, while HPCL fell 25% amid crude price spikes.","url":"https://tradebrains.in/5-stocks-from-key-sectors-that-fell-25-due-to-the-direct-impact-of-the-middle-east-conflict/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-24T05:15:28","source":"Trade Brains"},{"id":"536951","title":"Crude oil prices dropped 10.1% to $96.06 after Trump paused Iran strikes; later rebounded to $101.\nBPCL, HPCL, IOCL, RIL, and Petronet LNG secure LPG and crude shipments amid Hormuz tensions.","summary":"Crude oil prices dropped 10.1% to $96.06 after Trump paused Iran strikes; later rebounded to $101.\nBPCL, HPCL, IOCL, RIL, and Petronet LNG secure LPG and crude shipments amid Hormuz tensions.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/markets/commodities/oil-plunges-as-trump-pauses-iran-strikes-indian-lpg-tankers-cross-hormuz-126032301216_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-23T21:01:08","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"260323179393591","title":"West Asia conflict pushes OMCs, including Hindustan Petroleum, to expand LPG storage facilities.\nLPG, being highly impacted by the conflict, drives aggressive storage site initiatives.","summary":"West Asia conflict pushes OMCs, including Hindustan Petroleum, to expand LPG storage facilities.\nLPG, being highly impacted by the conflict, drives aggressive storage site initiatives.","url":"https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/economy/as-west-asia-conflict-intensifies-omcs-to-push-for-more-lpg-storage-facilities/article70776174.ece","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-23T20:04:11","source":"The Hindu BusinessLine"},{"id":"535927","titl